Recurrence Relation : 

T(n) = {
        O(1)  if n=1
        O(n) [partition] + T(m-l) + T(r-m)  if n>1
}

Time Complexity : 
best case & Average case = O(n) + T(n/2) + T(n/2)
          =  T(n/2) + n
          = O( n.logn )

worst case = O(n) + T(0) + T(n-1)
            = T(n-1) + n
            = O( n^2 )  [ for almost sorted array ]

